Package storm2013.commands

Class Summary
DoNothing Does nothing.
EncoderDrive Drives straight forward/back until a desired encoder value is reached.
FeederTurn Turn back/forth from feeder station.
GyroTurn Turns the robot until a desired heading is reached.
LowerTilter Moves the tilter downward.
MoveTilter Moves the tilter based on user input as configured in OI
PrintAutonomousMove Prints out code to be used in a CommandGroup for autonomous movement.
RaiseTilter Moves the tilter upward.
Shoot Spins up the shooter, then spins the tomahawk once when it is up to speed.
SpinDown Spins down the shooter wheel (and waits for it to stop).
SpinTomahawk Spins the tomahawk 1 revolution; sets the LED color as it does.
SpinUp Spins up the firing wheel, and waits for it to be on target.
StringPotTilt  
TankDrive Drives the robot based on joystick input (each side gets one axis).
TargetPIDCommand Base for TargetPIDTilt and TargetPIDTurn
TargetPIDTilt Does vertical target tracking (with the tilter).
TargetPIDTurn Does horizontal target tracking (turning the robot).
TiltCycleDistance  
TiltForDistance  
TiltSetDistance  
TiltToCurrentDistance
